How to install into a pylons(/django?) app
===============================================

1. Install middleware to env/venv
python setup.py install

2. Enable middleware in web app:
vim ./config/middleware.py

from oboeware import OboeMiddleware

...

    # Routing/Session/Cache Middleware
    app = RoutesMiddleware(app, config['routes.map'], singleton=False)
>>> app = OboeMiddleware(app, config)

    app = make_gzip_middleware(app, config)

    app = SessionMiddleware(app, config)
